{"type":"message","id":"0d1881c7","parentId":"15eaff42","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:24:07.663Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I found the key info. Let me search for the specific conversation about the preview link and the 17开头 id. From the session corpus, I can see that:\n\n1. The TikTok product ID format is 19 digits (like `1735209127318684977`)\n2. There's a preview URL template: `https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/1735209127318684977?encode_params=...`\n3. The user mentioned they have a preview link that I should concatenate with the ID\n\nThe user says \"有一个id是17开头的\" - wait, actually looking at the current message, the user says \"你能获取到一个id 是17开头的\" - but from the historical data, TikTok product IDs are 19 digits starting with 17...\n\n\nWait, the user might be saying the ID starts with 17. Looking at the examples from the corpus - `1735209127318684977` - yes that starts with 17. And they said \"我给过你一个预览连接，你直接拼接上就可以\" - there's a preview URL where I just need to concatenate the ID.\n\nSo the task now is:\n1. Rename the attachment to the TikTok product link\n2. Try to change the \"单选\" field to 1688 main image (using Sorftime MCP to get the image)\n3. Default status should be \"待审批\"\n\nI need to check the Feishu bitable skill to understand the current structure and field names.","thinkingSignature":"771921d3044b9d0b80549186c2a165e36b71a9f55d20bfd76bee70e936aa7d29"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到上下文了。从历史记录可以看到：\n\n- TikTok 产品 ID 是 19 位数字（如 `1735209127318684977`）\n- 预览链接模板：`https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/{id}?encode_params=...`\n- 需要通过 Sorftime MCP 获取 1688 主图\n- 状态默认\"待审批\"\n\n让我读取飞书多维表格的当前配置，看看字段情况。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_te8ex3fkyin0_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/feishu-doc/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2310,"output":434,"cacheRead":32288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35032,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779024237866,"responseId":"0658f46ea8369b39a3e93a85a4682523"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fd12a61d","parentId":"0d1881c7","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:24:07.668Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_te8ex3fkyin0_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-doc\ndescription: |\n  Feishu document read/write operations. Activate when user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or docx links.\n---\n\n# Feishu Document Tool\n\nSingle tool `feishu_doc` with action parameter for all document operations, including table creation for Docx.\n\n## Token Extraction\n\nFrom URL `https://xxx.feishu.cn/docx/ABC123def` → `doc_token` = `ABC123def`\n\n## Actions\n\n### Read Document\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"read\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\" }\n```\n\nReturns: title, plain text content, block statistics. Check `hint` field - if present, structured content (tables, images) exists that requires `list_blocks`.\n\n### Write Document (Replace All)\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"write\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"# Title\\n\\nMarkdown content...\" }\n```\n\nReplaces entire document with markdown content. Supports: headings, lists, code blocks, quotes, links, images (`![](url)` auto-uploaded), bold/italic/strikethrough.\n\n**Limitation:** Markdown tables are NOT supported.\n\n### Append Content\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"append\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"Additional content\" }\n```\n\nAppends markdown to end of document.\n\n### Create Document\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"create\", \"title\": \"New Document\", \"owner_open_id\": \"ou_xxx\" }\n```\n\nWith folder:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create\",\n  \"title\": \"New Document\",\n  \"folder_token\": \"fldcnXXX\",\n  \"owner_open_id\": \"ou_xxx\"\n}\n```\n\n**Important:** Always pass `owner_open_id` with the requesting user's `open_id` (from inbound metadata `sender_id`) so the user automatically gets `full_access` permission on the created document. Without this, only the bot app has access.\n\n### List Blocks\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"list_blocks\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\" }\n```\n\nReturns full block data including tables, images. Use this to read structured content.\n\n### Get Single Block\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"get_block\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\" }\n```\n\n### Update Block Text\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"update_block\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\",\n  \"content\": \"New text\"\n}\n```\n\n### Delete Block\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"delete_block\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\" }\n```\n\n### Create Table (Docx Table Block)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create_table\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"row_size\": 2,\n  \"column_size\": 2,\n  \"column_width\": [200, 200]\n}\n```\n\nOptional: `parent_block_id` to insert under a specific block.\n\n### Write Table Cells\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"write_table_cells\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"table_block_id\": \"doxcnTABLE\",\n  \"values\": [\n    [\"A1\", \"B1\"],\n    [\"A2\", \"B2\"]\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### Create Table With Values (One-step)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create_table_with_values\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"row_size\": 2,\n  \"column_size\": 2,\n  \"column_width\": [200, 200],\n  \"values\": [\n    [\"A1\", \"B1\"],\n    [\"A2\", \"B2\"]\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nOptional: `parent_block_id` to insert under a specific block.\n\n### Upload Image to Docx (from URL or local file)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_image\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"url\": \"https://example.com/image.png\"\n}\n```\n\nOr local path with position control:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_image\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"file_path\": \"/tmp/image.png\",\n  \"parent_block_id\": \"doxcnParent\",\n  \"index\": 5\n}\n```\n\nOptional `index` (0-based) inserts the image at a specific position among sibling blocks. Omit to append at end.\n\n**Note:** Image display size is determined by the uploaded image's pixel dimensions. For small images (e.g. 480x270 GIFs), scale to 800px+ width before uploading to ensure proper display.\n\n### Upload File Attachment to Docx (from URL or local file)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_file\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"url\": \"https://example.com/report.pdf\"\n}\n```\n\nOr local path:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_file\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"file_path\": \"/tmp/report.pdf\",\n  \"filename\": \"Q1-report.pdf\"\n}\n```\n\nRules:\n\n- exactly one of `url` / `file_path`\n- optional `filename` override\n- optional `parent_block_id`\n\n## Reading Workflow\n\n1. Start with `action: \"read\"` - get plain text + statistics\n2. Check `block_types` in response for Table, Image, Code, etc.\n3. If structured content exists, use `action: \"list_blocks\"` for full data\n\n## Configuration\n\n```yaml\nchannels:\n  feishu:\n    tools:\n      doc: true # default: true\n```\n\n**Note:** `feishu_wiki` depends on this tool - wiki page content is read/written via `feishu_doc`.\n\n## Permissions\n\nRequired: `docx:document`, `docx:document:readonly`, `docx:document.block:convert`, `drive:drive`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779024247668}}
{"type":"message","id":"eeecc1bd","parentId":"fd12a61d","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:24:23.735Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The feishu-doc skill only supports Feishu Docx documents, not Feishu Base (multidimensional table / bitable). The user's data is in a Feishu Base table (bitable). Let me check the mcporter skill to see if there's a sorftime MCP tool to get product images.\n\nActually, from what I recall from the conversation history, the key things I need to figure out are:\n\n1. **Attachment name → TikTok product link**: The user wants the \"附件\" (attachment) field to contain the TikTok product URL. The TikTok product link format is `https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/{id}` where the ID starts with 17. The user mentioned there was a preview URL where we just need to concatenate the ID.\n\n\n2. **Single select → 1688 main image**: The \"单选\" (single select) field should be set to the 1688 product's main image, which can be retrieved through the Sorftime MCP tool.\n3. **Default status → pending approval**: The \"采集状态\" (collection status) field should default to \"待审批\" (pending approval).\n\nLet me try using the mcporter tool to call the sorftime MCP and get the images. I should also look for the preview URL pattern in the session corpus.\n\nActually, the preview URL pattern seems to follow the format `https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/{product_id}`, so I need to search the session corpus for where this preview link template was originally shared so I can properly construct the product URL.","thinkingSignature":"e0cfd09158b522ce2643dce5cafb0d69b7865103ddc9d55e17b97230f9d86a8a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b9d81z6mogal_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"tiktok.com/view/product\\|encode_params\\|预览.*链接\\|拼接\" /home/halei/workspace-tts/memory/.dreams/session-corpus/2026-05-10.txt 2>/dev/null | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1332,"output":397,"cacheRead":34592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36321,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779024247689,"responseId":"0658f477f1df72926fa7588ebef00487"}}
