{"type":"message","id":"5df6ca3d","parentId":"0ab274f0","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:24:51.234Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to find more recent context about the specific items the user is asking me to do. The user is saying:\n1. 附件名字改为tiktok的商品链接 - Change attachment name to TikTok product link\n2. 能获取到一个id是17开头的 - There's an ID starting with 17\n3. 我给过你一个预览连接，你直接拼接上就可以 - I gave you a preview link, just concatenate the ID\n4. 单选，可以尝试改为1688的主图 - The single select field can try to be changed to 1688 main image\n5. 状态默认的都是待审批 - Status default is \"pending approval\"\n\nSo this sounds like we're modifying the write logic for the Feishu spreadsheet, changing:\n\n\n- \"附件\" field: fill with TikTok product link (concatenated from preview URL + 17-prefixed ID)\n- \"单选\" field: try to fill with 1688 main image URL\n- \"状态\" field: default to \"待审批\"\n\nI need to find the most recent conversation where these specific modifications were being discussed.\n","thinkingSignature":"ddbb36dbd8e7bbda2a363e6dcc669076c9604e35ceae4a75fc5c9e2716dc3a63"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p0ltcrpsgzxd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"单选\\|待审批\\|附件.*链接\\|tiktok.*链接\" /home/halei/workspace-tts/memory/.dreams/session-corpus/2026-05-15.txt 2>/dev/null | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":442,"output":303,"cacheRead":36864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37609,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779024282058,"responseId":"0658f49a238129970fcb2436f36356ae"}}
