{"type":"message","id":"cebbfd73","parentId":"eb3ba5a5","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:25:33.897Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_s3mrr4xpbv6l_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"sorftime-mcp\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://mcp.sorftime.com/\",\n      \"headers\": {\n        \"Authorization\": \"Bearer zwpmsm…zz09\",\n        \"accept\": \"application/json, text/event-stream\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"sorftime-test\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://mcp.sorftime.com/\",\n      \"headers\": {\n        \"Authorization\": \"Bearer rhblyi…qt09\",\n        \"accept\": \"application/json, text/event-stream\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":12,"aggregated":"{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"sorftime-mcp\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://mcp.sorftime.com/\",\n      \"headers\": {\n        \"Authorization\": \"Bearer zwpmsmvutwvimcs2mmlzu2vyl3dkzz09\",\n        \"accept\": \"application/json, text/event-stream\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"sorftime-test\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://mcp.sorftime.com/\",\n      \"headers\": {\n        \"Authorization\": \"Bearer rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09\",\n        \"accept\": \"application/json, text/event-stream\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}","cwd":"/home/halei/workspace-tts"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779024333897}}
{"type":"message","id":"5488a37f","parentId":"cebbfd73","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:25:41.867Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to find the current 飞书 table structure to understand the fields. Let me use the feishu-wiki or some feishu tool to get the table metadata. But I notice the user mentioned the table has a \"单选\" field for 1688 main image. \n\nActually, wait - looking at the context again:\n\n\"单选，可以尝试改为1688的主图\" - The user is saying the \"单选\" field (radio selection) could be changed to use the 1688 main image.\n\nAnd \"状态默认的都是都是待审批哈\" - The status defaults to \"待审批\" (pending approval).\n \nSo the user wants me to write data to the 飞书 table at https://my.feishu.cn/base/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd, where the attachment field gets renamed to use the TikTok product link, I pull the 1688 main image for the radio selection field, and set the status to pending approval by default. I need to fetch the current table schema first to see how these fields are structured.","thinkingSignature":"fc9cf7487c2bb7572ea5b4403ea534d62de77f713f0c65d03e090b680655406d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1k5hmvigpszc_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/feishu-wiki/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":207,"output":269,"cacheRead":38080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38556,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779024333939,"responseId":"0658f4ced6a0100d213cff0f2ac1d9e2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7da700c3","parentId":"5488a37f","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:25:41.872Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1k5hmvigpszc_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-wiki\ndescription: |\n  Feishu knowledge base navigation. Activate when user mentions knowledge base, wiki, or wiki links.\n---\n\n# Feishu Wiki Tool\n\nSingle tool `feishu_wiki` for knowledge base operations.\n\n## Token Extraction\n\nFrom URL `https://xxx.feishu.cn/wiki/ABC123def` → `token` = `ABC123def`\n\n## Actions\n\n### List Knowledge Spaces\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"spaces\" }\n```\n\nReturns all accessible wiki spaces.\n\n### List Nodes\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"nodes\", \"space_id\": \"7xxx\" }\n```\n\nWith parent:\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"nodes\", \"space_id\": \"7xxx\", \"parent_node_token\": \"wikcnXXX\" }\n```\n\n### Get Node Details\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"get\", \"token\": \"***\" }\n```\n\nReturns: `node_token`, `obj_token`, `obj_type`, etc. Use `obj_token` with `feishu_doc` to read/write the document.\n\n### Create Node\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"create\", \"space_id\": \"7xxx\", \"title\": \"New Page\" }\n```\n\nWith type and parent:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create\",\n  \"space_id\": \"7xxx\",\n  \"title\": \"Sheet\",\n  \"obj_type\": \"sheet\",\n  \"parent_node_token\": \"wikcnXXX\"\n}\n```\n\n`obj_type`: `docx` (default), `sheet`, `bitable`, `mindnote`, `file`, `doc`, `slides`\n\n### Move Node\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"move\", \"space_id\": \"7xxx\", \"node_token\": \"wikcnXXX\" }\n```\n\nTo different location:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"move\",\n  \"space_id\": \"7xxx\",\n  \"node_token\": \"wikcnXXX\",\n  \"target_space_id\": \"7yyy\",\n  \"target_parent_token\": \"wikcnYYY\"\n}\n```\n\n### Rename Node\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"rename\", \"space_id\": \"7xxx\", \"node_token\": \"wikcnXXX\", \"title\": \"New Title\" }\n```\n\n## Wiki-Doc Workflow\n\nTo edit a wiki page:\n\n1. Get node: `{ \"action\": \"get\", \"token\": \"***\" }` → returns `obj_token`\n2. Read doc: `feishu_doc { \"action\": \"read\", \"doc_token\": \"obj_token\" }`\n3. Write doc: `feishu_doc { \"action\": \"write\", \"doc_token\": \"obj_token\", \"content\": \"...\" }`\n\n## Configuration\n\n```yaml\nchannels:\n  feishu:\n    tools:\n      wiki: true # default: true\n      doc: true # required - wiki content uses feishu_doc\n```\n\n**Dependency:** This tool requires `feishu_doc` to be enabled. Wiki pages are documents - use `feishu_wiki` to navigate, then `feishu_doc` to read/edit content.\n\n## Permissions\n\nRequired: `wiki:wiki` or `wiki:wiki:readonly`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779024341871}}
