{"type":"message","id":"c3fee2df","parentId":"6daa3c21","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:30:27.346Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full preview URL template:\n\n```\nhttps://www.tiktok.com/view/product/{ID}?encode_params=MIIBpgQMjR-IK7WIIdcHbnksBIIBghIkiv11tlKb3-ikvTwrfaU3AVqwQC73XL3LBhQX9Yi9RbNQxbpDR7cs9LLpU9ZDgHip1627I0qVsAbulNS1_Qibv_JCOJpfQO_Cws-38pDnzX3pL6CD8_AMkAg4X-jOcGyLzWnmyXPrg7cUzljqpGktHvpFvXgnQNZpB9OCKiD1yaaV0mdCNZ_cELquznIQtMi8jFWDFZ08R2SSDkt0qfvGQhm6Sq0Oj7o0soPULYJMQtTmN8RCccOCnBZYldt7Z_HDo7HJRiOZ8NdqBW1zzKtBOmGAEAF_M5hdigdwrZMVYe_KouITOp8OCDtt0n6E5tElVdi49Nz7dElpe2Dfv5026SrYH0FecZrVbxRIcDzWJt7MEFquXk16eG69ze0Z2RUy3IP6rlv7-INOjJZXGcWHvVkV8Stst_hiMifmzgam1B6boNdvkTWK5R0P_SZvOufeHIAIMxegKNyvWmIL2sspyXJVTtMQ14vKvHwwuUYc3b0yufpSAJI8d14sPFvYqoyfBBC0cTF3hcwCRopBVm88nbtp&region=VN&locale=zh-CN&source=seller_center&hide_tips=&no-cache=1&e=1\n\n\n```\n\nThe URL template is confirmed to work—it's the same structure as before with the fixed encode_params and other query parameters. So for any TikTok product ID, I just swap it into the `{ID}` placeholder and the URL will work. I should also check if there's a 1688 product link format I need to handle similarly.\n\nLooking back at what the user mentioned, they want the \"单选\" field changed to the 1688 main image URL instead of the current TikTok product URL. And regarding the link format, they said the previous format I set up for the 1688 product links using the `{\"link\": \"url\", \"text\": \"name\"}` structure was good—they don't want me to change that approach.\n\n```\n{\"link\": \"https://...\", \"text\": \"商品名称\"}\n```\n\nThis is the rich link format that Feishu supports for clickable hyperlinks. I need to search through the conversation history to find what the \"单选\" field actually represents and what value should go there.\n\n```","thinkingSignature":"8839b4773eb4c1297e953be9e9a567542e907628473a25e521561d1125608e77"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_functio