{"type":"message","id":"12bd525a","parentId":"10c54b32","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:30:34.060Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the structure. The current fields are:\n1. 日期 (Date)\n2. 站点 (Site)\n3. 附件 (Attachment) - should be TikTok product link with hyperlink\n4. 商品名称 (Product Name)\n5. 售价（本地货币）(Price in local currency)\n6. 增长率 (Growth rate)\n7. 月销量 (Monthly sales)\n8. 利润率(%) (Profit margin %)\n9. 1688同款链接 (1688 same product link) - already has hyperlink format\n\n\n10. 单选 (Single choice) - try to use 1688 main image\n11. 三级类目 (Level 3 category)\n12. 1688价格(CNY) (1688 price in CNY)\n13. 预估利润 (Estimated profit)\n14. 推荐等级 (Recommendation level)\n15. 采集状态 (Collection status) - default \"待审批\"\n16. IP风险 (IP risk)\n17. 行动建议 (Action recommendation)\n\nI need to update the data for these three fields: the attachment should show the TikTok product link with the text \"TK商品链接\" and a hyperlink, the single choice field should contain the 1688 main image, and the collection status should default to \"待审批\". Since the Sorftime API key is currently having issues, I'll need to work around that limitation.\n","thinkingSignature":"ee8703c9e8df65ebc35ccb44b93edbe0fe5386ae3f254f7b5ddede7fd80f9d04"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白了！URL格式就是 `https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/{ID}?encode_params=...`，ID替换即可。链接写成超链格式。\n\n现在让我先测试 Sorftime MCP 能否正常调用，然后写入数据：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wunmj8ww3ccm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-test.tiktok_category_report country_code:VN category_id:908552 time_range:30 --output json 2>/dev/null | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":258,"output":388,"cacheRead":43104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43750,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779024627598,"responseId":"0658f5f4437165cc1997a1cda8347f6f"}}
