titles like \"Kẹp Chuối Lười...\" rather than English Amazon descriptions. So I should focus on finding which TikTok API endpoints return ProductId, likely starting with `tiktok_product_detail`.\n\nLet me run a test query to see what specific product details I can pull using one of the top product titles from the category report. I'm realizing the core issue: the category report gives me product titles but no IDs, and Sorftime's similar product search seems to be returning Amazon data instead of actual TikTok products. I should just test the `tiktok_product_detail` function directly with a known TikTok product ID to see what information it actually returns.\n\nThe user confirmed that `tiktok_product_detail` does return ProductId like \"1731002875688620178\" - that's the 19-digit TikTok format I need. So the priority is finding a way to get those ProductIds from the category report data. I'm recalling that when we searched for similar products before, we got ProductId in the results. The issue is that the category report endpoint doesn't return product IDs directly. I should suggest a workflow where we pull products from the category report, then use the product title to search via `tiktok_similar_product` to get the actual product IDs and details we need. 链接的格式（商品名称作为文字，URL作为超链接）\n\n我需要确认一下Sorftime MCP中哪些接口能返回TikTok产品ID。根据schema检查，`tiktok_category_report` 只返回标题，`tiktok_product_video` 可能返回产品ID，但我需要先测试一下这个接口是否能获取到产品ID。\n","thinkingSignature":"5c21b73c52adda913b99938e4a48b053540900a4a722197e240f825538104f3a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n你说得对！产品ID就是这种19位数字格式，我之前混淆了——`tiktok_category_report` 的Top50没有返回ProductId，但 `tiktok_product_detail` 这种接口是有的。\n\n让我测试一下哪些接口能返回产品ID：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k67yrq1krxra_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-test.tiktok_product_detail productId:\"1731002875688620178\" --output json 2>/dev/null | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | head -80"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","mode