{"type":"message","id":"b622438a","parentId":"65095c09","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:38:27.166Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found the TikTok product IDs! The `tiktok_similar_product` tool returns `ProductId` field with 17-digit IDs like `1732160188396766700`. Now I can construct TikTok preview links like the user described.\n\nNow I need to construct the full TikTok product link format:\n`https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/1735607232978388273?encode_params=MIIBpgQMjR-IK7WIIdcHbnksBIIBghIkiv11tlKb3-ikvTwrfaU3AVqwQC73XL3LBhQX9Yi9RbNQxbpDR7cs9LLpU9ZDgHip1627I0qVsAbulNS1_Qibv_JCOJpfQO_Cws-38pDnzX3pL6CD8_AMkAg4X-jOcGyLzWnmyXPrg7cUzljqpGktHvpFvXgnQNZpB9OCKiD1yaaV0mdCNZ_cELquznIQtMi8jFWDFZ08R2SSDkt0qfvGQhm6Sq0Oj7o0soPULYJMQtTmN8RCccOCnBZYldt7Z_HDo7HJRiOZ8NdqBW1zzKtBOmGAEAF_M5hdigdwrZMVYe_KouITOp8OCDtt0n6E5tElVdi49Nz7dElpe2Dfv5026SrYH0FecZrVbxRIcDzWJt7MEFquXk16eG69ze0Z2RUy3IP6rlv7-INOjJZXGcWHvVkV8Stst\n\n_hiMifmzgam1B6boNdvkTWK5R0P_SZvOufeHIAIMxegKNyvWmIL2sspyXJVTtMQ14vKvHwwuUYc3b0yufpSAJI8d14sPFvYqoyfBBC0cTF3hcwCRopBVm88nbtp&region=VN&locale=zh-CN&source=seller_center&hide_tips=&no-cache=1&e=1`\n\nThe user mentioned their encode_params stays constant across IDs, so I just swap out the product ID portion. The other query parameters like region and locale remain unchanged.\n\nNow I'm looking at the core requirements: update the attachment field with the TikTok link in hyperlink format, pull the main image from 1688 instead, and set a default status field. I need to figure out how to actually write these records to the Feishu base.\n\nLooking at my available tools, `feishu_doc` only handles documents, not base tables. I remember the user had already granted permissions for table operations, so there might be a `bitable` tool available. Let me check what tools are configured in the OpenClaw setup.\n","thinkingSignature":"4a99d49665940259406f33afb07dcf19334a0ca993288e2c8b02208dd1b3e359"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到了！`ProductId` 就是