{"type":"message","id":"b626251f","parentId":"3385d8eb","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:40:50.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the format. Looking at the existing data:\n\n1. **附件** (field_id: fldxbLqnvR, type: 17 Attachment) - Currently empty. The user wants this to contain the TikTok product link. But Attachments in Feishu are files/images, not URLs. However, looking at the 1688同款链接 field, it uses `{\"link\": \"...\", \"text\": \"...\"}` format - but that's a URL type (type 15), not Attachment.\n\nWait, the user said \"附件名字改为tiktok的商品链接\" - they want the attachment NAME to be the TikTok product link. But Attachments store files. Maybe they mean they want to add a file attachment with the product link URL as the filename? Or maybe they want me to upload a text file with the link?\n \nI think there's a distinction here between the 附件 field itself (which is meant for file attachments) and the 1688同款链接 field (which is a URL type that supports the `{\"link\": \"...\", \"text\": \"...\"}` format). The user might be asking to use the attachment field differently - perhaps they want to create a file whose name is the TikTok product link, or they're conflating the two fields and actually want the URL field to contain the TikTok link instead. to use the URL field to store the TikTok product link with the same link format they mentioned. They said not to use the URL field that way though, which contradicts what I'm seeing in the data structure where the URL field already has that link format. Maybe they're referring to the 单选 field instead and want me to handle things differently than before. Looking at the field structure more carefully, the user wants me to update the existing 6 records by changing the \"附件\" field to contain TikTok product links instead of empty values. The challenge is that 附件 is an Attachment type field, so I need to figure out how to properly format the TikTok URL link within Feishu's attachment field structure. the 附件 field to contain text or a link. Actually, in Feishu bitable, the Attachment field type only accepts actual file uploads, not text or URLs. There's no way to write a link directly to an Attachment field. So I need to reconsider - maybe the user actually wants the TikTok product link in the \"1688同款链接\" field instead, which is a proper URL field that supports links. Let me check the existing record structure to understand what's currently there and what format the links are in.\n\nLooking at the current data, that field already has 1688 links, so I should clarify with the user whether they want to replace those with TikTok links, or if they want both, or if \"附件\" is actually referring to something else. Given they mentioned \"单选\" can try 1688 main image instead, I think the most practical solution is to put the TikTok product link as a URL in the existing field since that's the supported format, and then try to handle the 1688 main image for the \"单选\" field by uploading the image or referencing it properly.\n","thinkingSignature":"057ac060d14a0c64ec5cd463aad0c9b8d053c1a237a1d847314d78716118a74c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的，我现在完全理解了。让我整理一下发现：\n\n**表头确认（17个字段）：**\n- 附件 (fldxbLqnvR) - type: Attachment（文件附件）\n- 1688同款链接 (fldvQ46B4r) - type: URL，支持 `{\"link\": \"...\", \"text\": \"...\"}` 格式\n- 单选 (fldIfpZo7P) - type: SingleSelect\n- 采集状态 (fldipZCSu3) - type: SingleSelect，当前值：待审批/已采集\n\n**问题：** 附件字段是 Attachment 类型（文件），不支持写入链接文字，只接受文件上传。\n\n**我的建议方案：**\n1. **附件** → 我尝试上传一个 `.txt` 文件，文件名就是 TikTok 产品链接\n2. **1688同款链接** → 保持现有格式，直接写入 TikTok 产品 URL（`https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/{ID}?encode_params=...`）\n3. **单选** → 尝试写入 1688 主图 URL（通过 `ali1688_similar_product` 获取）\n4. **采集状态** → 默认写入\"待审批\"\n\n但我现在遇到一个问题——**附件类型不能直接写文字，需要先上传文件**。你确定要把 TikTok 链接放在附件字段吗？还是建议放到\"1688同款链接\"那个 URL 字段里？那个字段格式是 `{\"link\": \"链接\", \"text\": \"显示文字\"}`，直接写入就行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1738,"output":968,"cacheRead":65344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68050,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779025231729,"responseId":"0658f8504c0e3cb8a500a0a8af84b818"}}
