{"type":"message","id":"d2f32876","parentId":"6ea78ed6","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:50:57.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The multi-select field was created successfully. Now the user wants me to write data to this table. But first, let me confirm the new field structure. Also, I need to handle the \"1688产品主图\" field which is an Attachment type - uploading images to Feishu bitable requires a separate upload process.\n\nLet me summarize what I've done and what needs to be done next.\n\nActually, I should also handle the issue of writing to the TK product link field and the 1688 product image field. But first, let me just confirm the success to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"8acdc00208a557e9df747911dd520f189b0d56f282f8eebf956e40396ad41c9f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n搞定了！✅\n\n**新增字段：选品来源** (多选)\n- `fldU6xEkIL`\n- 支持多选，可选：Sorftime / 1688直选 / 亚马逊爆款跟随 / TikTok爆款跟随 / 竞品监控 / 工厂定制 / 网红带货同款\n\n---\n\n现在写入数据时需要确认几个问题：\n\n1. **TK产品连接** (URL) → 你已经改好格式了，我直接写 `{\"link\": \"https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/{ID}?encode_params=...\", \"text\": \"产品名称\"}` 就行\n\n2. **1688产品主图** (Attachment) → 这个需要先上传图片获取 token，再写入。我需要先下载 1688 图片再上传到飞书，这个流程稍复杂\n\n3. **采集状态** → 默认写入\"待审批\" ✅\n\n你想让我先拿哪条候选品跑一遍写入流程？把产品名或TikTok产品ID给我就行 👇"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":873,"output":333,"cacheRead":69920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71126,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779025849511,"responseId":"0658faba6c968252c4b8bd365b30e596"}}
