{"type":"message","id":"eb9e58d5","parentId":"1d121b46","timestamp":"2026-05-17T13:54:34.576Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to:\n1. Add \"TikTok爆款跟随\" as a separate selection source option (already done in my previous field creation)\n2. Rename the existing options to make them more accurate - the user is saying \"轨道1\" is about \"数据驱动下的综合选品\" not just Sorftime\n3. They want to add a key parameter to filter what kind of TikTok hot products to follow - to prevent blind following\n\nLet me think about what the user means:\n- \"TikTok爆款跟随\" - already in my list, so that's fine\n- 轨道1 should be \"数据驱动综合选品\" - this is about using multiple data sources (Sorftime, EchoTik, TK data) to make comprehensive selection decisions\n\n\n- They want a data-driven screening parameter to filter TikTok products before following them, rather than blindly chasing every viral item - something like minimum monthly sales, growth rate, or review count thresholds to identify genuinely promising products worth following instead of just copying everything.\n\nNow I'm looking at the existing selection source options to see if they need renaming or consolidation, since some overlap with the three-track strategy framework I outlined earlier. 1688直选\" as its own track\n- \"亚马逊爆款跟随\" - from track 2\n- \"TikTok爆款跟随\" - from track 2\n- \"竞品监控\" - from track 2\n- \"工厂定制\" - special\n- \"网红带货同款\" - special\n\nThe user seems to want to keep these options but clarify the naming. Let me respond about the key parameter for TikTok爆款跟随.\n\nActually, let me re-read the user's message more carefully. They're saying TikTok爆款跟随 should be added as a separate option, and they're pointing out that 轨道1 is about data-driven comprehensive selection (not just Sorftime). They also want a key screening parameter to prevent blind following.\n\nFor the key parameter, based on the SOP, the key TikTok following parameters could be:\n1. 月销量 ≥ 某个值 (e.g., ≥500 or ≥1000)\n