{"type":"message","id":"0da32751","parentId":"06e70b85","timestamp":"2026-05-17T14:01:19.457Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to:\n1. Remove \"竞品监控\", \"工厂定制\", \"网红带货同款\" from the field options\n2. Update the SOP with the new selection strategy\n\nLet me first update the field options (delete the last 3), then update the SOP.md file.\n\nFor the field, I need to update the options for \"选品来源\" field. I'll need to update it with only the 4 options: Sorftime, 1688直选, 亚马逊爆款跟随, TikTok爆款跟随.\n\nFor the SOP, I need to incorporate the new strategy insights:\n- 轨道1 = 数据驱动综合选品 (Sorftime)\n\n\n- 轨道2 = 爆款跟随 with guard parameters:\n  - TikTok爆款跟随: 增长率 > 0\n  - 亚马逊爆款跟随: 月销量 ≥ 1000\n- 轨道3 = 1688直选\n\nLet me do both tasks.","thinkingSignature":"1fb35e0378546552fb16b550204d55b8aa86a03f4e9fa51e3644ab39e45d00e3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3kzrezdtqdx5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TOKEN=\"t-g1045hlaEG4G4G33TKPZQOQYI7VSPVEL47LLTYGA\"\nAPP_TOKEN=\"AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\"\nTABLE_ID=\"tblHU2do30jzinJT\"\n\n# 更新选品来源字段，只保留4个选项\ncurl -s -X PUT \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bitable/v1/apps/${APP_TOKEN}/tables/${TABLE_ID}/fields/fldU6xEkIL\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer ${TOKEN}\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"field_name\": \"选品来源\",\n    \"type\": 4,\n    \"property\": {\n      \"options\": [\n        {\"name\": \"Sorftime（数据驱动）\", \"color\": 0},\n        {\"name\": \"1688直选\", \"color\": 1},\n        {\"name\": \"亚马逊爆款跟随\", \"color\": 2},\n        {\"name\": \"TikTok爆款跟随\", \"color\": 3}\n      ]\n    }\n  }' 2>/dev/null | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":78026,"output":482,"cacheRead":1024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79532,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779026468437,"responseId":"0658fd2532d0affb7