{"type":"message","id":"fc5860a2","parentId":"d085e636","timestamp":"2026-05-17T14:03:57.151Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Now the field is renamed to \"产品连接\" which is more generic and can include TikTok, Amazon, or any other platform links.\n","thinkingSignature":"c54a9bca06b3b1020116cfb562054c9f53f73407ecb3692cd0005d913ee55407"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n对，改了：\n\n**字段名：** `TK产品连接` → `产品连接` ✅\n\n这样亚马逊链接也能写进去了，通用性更好。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":383,"output":64,"cacheRead":103488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103935,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779026618514,"responseId":"0658fdba9dd3cd4ea5f73883e98e093f"}}
