{"type":"message","id":"cba2fe40","parentId":"73a6127e","timestamp":"2026-05-17T14:04:29.719Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is confirming that product selection data still comes from Sorftime (since Sorftime provides both Amazon and TikTok data), and the \"产品连接\" field is just the URL field for the product link. They want to confirm that Sorftime is the unified data source for both Amazon and TikTok products.\n\nThis makes sense - Sorftime MCP has tools for:\n- TikTok: tiktok_category_report, tiktok_similar_product, tiktok_product_detail\n- Amazon: similar_product_feature (for Amazon product research)\n\nSo the \"选品来源\" field would be \"Sorftime（数据驱动）\" regardless of whether it's TK or Amazon data. The \"产品连接\" field would store the actual product URL (TK or Amazon).\n\n\nI should confirm this understanding and ask if they're ready to start writing data to the table.\n","thinkingSignature":"31beec1cd2844a14bef2ab433705a0d1f1d5beb5262fb2183d8bf40e64e8396d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n对，Sorftime 本身就同时支持 TikTok 和亚马逊数据，所以选品来源统一填 `Sorftime（数据驱动）`，不用区分 TK 还是 Amazon。\n\n产品连接字段写入对应的平台链接就行（TK 链接格式 / Amazon 链接格式都可以）。\n\n字段配置现在是这样：\n- **选品来源** → `Sorftime（数据驱动）`（统一来源）\n- **产品连接** → 写入 TikTok 或 Amazon 产品链接（URL 超链格式）\n- **1688产品主图** → 写入 1688 附件图片\n- **采集状态** → 默认\"待审批\"\n\n数据格式都理清了。现在要开始写入候选品了吗？把产品名称或者 TikTok 产品 ID 发过来，我跑一遍写入流程 👇"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":203,"output":326,"cacheRead":103808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104337,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779026649850,"responseId":"0658fdda92dde1f3b017b7530ab4d604"}}
