{"type":"message","id":"916814fb","parentId":"21085833","timestamp":"2026-05-17T14:05:09.650Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about setting a target of 10 products selected per day. This makes sense given:\n- They have a table with various fields\n- They're running a TTS agent focused on TikTok product selection for Vietnam market\n- They want a daily quota of 10 products to select\n\nI should confirm this and ask about the workflow - do they want me to run the selection automatically each day? What's the trigger? When do they want this to happen?\n\nKey questions:\n1. Do they want me to run automatically at a specific time each day?\n2. Should I notify them after completing the selection?\n3. What's the criteria for the 10 products (top 10 by score? something else?)\n\nThe SOP already has a work rhythm section that mentions:\n- 9:00-9:45: Automatic selection process\n- 10:00: Sync to Feishu + push notification\n\nSo perhaps I should align with that existing rhythm. But they might want to adjust the number to 10.\n\nLet me confirm the 10 products/day target and ask about the timing/workflow.\n","thinkingSignature":"82bdb47ed2b7a35e64742c8d77992df772aa9d37a9d9f9e29c10056c7079668d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，定量：**每天选出 10 个候选品入库**。\n\n结合 SOP 里的工作节奏，可以这样安排：\n\n**每日流程：**\n1. **9:00** — 自动跑 Sorftime → 选品数据（VN 站 Hair Clips 类目 Top50）\n2. **9:00-9:45** — 按 SOP 流程过滤：参数卡死 → 三步验证 → 综合评分 → 排序 Top10\n3. **10:00** — 写入飞书表格（10 条），推送通知给你\n\n**筛选标准（Top10 排序逻辑）：**\n- 综合评分 ≥ 100 分\n- 增长率 > 0\n- 毛利率 ≥ 30%\n- 采集状态默认\"待审批\"\n\n**你确认一下：**\n1. ✅ 每天 10 条这个量 OK 吗？\n2. ✅ 自动跑的时间（早上 9 点）合适吗？还是你想其他时间？\n3. ✅ 我跑完后直接写入飞书，然后通知你，还是你希望先预览再确认？\n\n确认后我就在 SOP 里把这个「每日 10 品」的目标和工作流程固化进去。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":405,"output":460,"cacheRead":104000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104865,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestam