{"type":"message","id":"da513ce7","parentId":"8decfe37","timestamp":"2026-05-17T14:11:04.768Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying:\n1. The selection source should be separated as: Sorftime, 亚马逊, TK (not just Sorftime)\n2. 10 products per day, at 9am, notify via Feishu - all confirmed\n\nSo I need to:\n1. Update the 选品来源 field options to be more specific - separate by platform data source (Sorftime data from Amazon, Sorftime data from TikTok, etc.)\n2. Update the SOP to reflect this\n3. Set up the daily workflow\n\nThe user wants to know the data source for each product - whether it came from Amazon data or TikTok data through Sorftime. So \"选品来源\" should distinguish:\n- TikTok数据（通过Sorftime）\n- 亚马逊数据（通过Sorftime）\n- 1688数据（通过Sorftime）\n\nWait but earlier the user said Sorftime is the unified data source. Now they want to distinguish based on the platform. So the source field should show which platform's data was used to select the product, even though Sorftime is the tool providing the data.\n\nSo 选品来源 options should be:\n- TikTok数据（通过Sorftime）- 亚马逊数据（通过Sorftime）\n- 1688数据（通过Sorftime）\n\n\n- 或者更直接：Sorftime-TK / Sorftime-亚马逊 / Sorftime-1688\n\nLet me update the field and SOP accordingly.\n\nThe user confirmed: 10 products, 9am, Feishu notification. They want the source field to reflect which platform the data came from (TikTok, Amazon, or 1688) even though Sorftime is providing the data. So I need to update the 选品来源 field options and then set up the daily workflow with Feishu notifications at 9am.\n","thinkingSignature":"58a78a12881c18841334aa62cc7348d0d872437f773dc7b441a679181e677130"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ah61pby3j5r0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TOKEN=\"t-g1045hlaEG4G4G33TKPZQOQYI7VSPVEL47LLTYGA\"\nAPP_TOKEN=\"AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\"\nTABLE_ID=\"tblHU2do30jzinJT\"\n\n# 更新选品来源字段，按平台来源区分\ncurl -s -X PUT \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bitable/v1/apps/${APP_TOKEN}/tables/${TA