{"type":"message","id":"bd654508","parentId":"2875143c","timestamp":"2026-05-17T14:12:24.838Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All updates done. Let me confirm to the user:\n1. 选品来源 field updated to: Sorftime-TK数据 / Sorftime-亚马逊数据 / Sorftime-1688数据\n2. SOP updated: 每日10品目标 + 工作节奏\n3. 10条/9点/飞书通知 都确认\n\nNow I should also mention that I should update the 三轨选品策略 section in SOP to reflect the new \"选品来源\" options as Sorftime-TK/亚马逊/1688 (all from Sorftime). The user clarified that Sorftime is the unified data source for all three, so the three tracks are actually:\n- Track 1: Sorftime-TK数据 (from Sorftime TikTok tools)\n\n\n- Track 2: Sorftime-亚马逊数据 (from Sorftime Amazon tools)\n- Track 3: Sorftime-1688数据 (from Sorftime 1688 tools)\n\nI need to update the 三轨选品策略 section to reflect this unified data source approach.\n","thinkingSignature":"5c90d8582b881b31cba568caafdb20186e6660a6505c578b6cf50f14da7ab964"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sd8w45j364d8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nwith open('/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP.md', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\nold = \"\"\"### 轨道 1：Sorftime（数据驱动综合选品）\n\n- **选品来源：** `Sorftime（数据驱动）`\n- **数据源：** Sorftime MCP → TikTok 类目报告 + 亚马逊爆款基因 + 1688 供应链\n- **筛选逻辑：** 参数卡死 → 三步快速验证 → 通用词延展 → 综合评分 → 保守测盈利\n- **核心优势：** 多维度数据交叉验证，不盲目跟品\n\n### 轨道 2：爆款跟随（数据锚点过滤）\n\n\n#### TikTok爆款跟随\n- **选品来源：** `TikTok爆款跟随`\n- **数据源：** Sorftime `tiktok_similar_product` → VN 站热搜品\n- **关键参数：** 增长率 > 0（月销量环比正增长，方能跟随。衰退品一律不跟）\n- **跟品红线：** 增长率 ≤ 0 的品不看，无论销量多高\n\n#### 亚马逊爆款跟随\n- **选品来源：** `亚马逊爆款跟随`\n- **数据源：** Sorftime `similar_product_feature` → 美区 Hair Claws 类目\n- **关键参数：** 月销量 ≥ 1000 + 上架 ≥ 6 个月（验证市场稳定性）\n- **筛选逻辑：** 体量达标 + 毛利率 ≥ 30% + 越南审美适配 + 三步验证\n\n### 轨道 3：1688 直选（供应链驱动）\n- **选品来源：** `1688直选`\n- **数据源：** Sorftime `ali1688_similar_product` → 1688 货源搜索\n- **筛选逻辑：** 进货价 ×3-15、一件代发、48h发货 → 三步验证 → 交叉验证\"\"\"\n\nnew = \"\"\"### 轨道 1：Sorftime-TK数据\n\n- **选品来源：** `Sorftime-TK数据`\n- **数据源：** Sorftime `tiktok_category_report` + `tiktok_similar_product` → VN 站\n- **筛选逻辑：** 参数卡死 → 三步快速验证 → 综合评分 → 保守测盈利\n\n### 轨道 2：Sorftime-亚马逊数据\n\n- **选品来源：** `Sorftime-亚马逊数据`\n- **数据源：** Sorftime `similar_product_feature` → 美区 Hair Claws 类目\n- **关键参数：** 月销量 ≥ 1000 + 上架 ≥ 6 个月\n- **筛选逻辑：** 体量达标 + 毛利率 ≥ 30% + 越南审美适配 + 三步验证\n\n### 轨道 3：Sorftime-1688数据\n\n- **选品来源：** `Sorftime-1688数据`\n- **数据源：** Sorftime `ali1688_similar_product` → 1688 货源\n- **筛选逻辑：** 进货价 ×3-15、一件代发、48h发货 → 三步验证 → 交叉验证\"\"\"\n\nif old in content:\n    content = content.replace(old, new)\n    with open('/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP.md', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        f.write(content)\n    print(\"SUCCESS: tracks updated\")\nelse:\n    print(\"NOT FOUND\")\n\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":366,"output":951,"cacheRead":105984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107301,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779027107704,"responseId":"0658ffa49775740f50d44c1db2ff6ab7"}}
