{"type":"message","id":"a78b0bcb","parentId":"fa325649","timestamp":"2026-05-17T14:19:37.714Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying:\n1. Use the fixed encode_params for now\n2. Don't select products now - wait for the scheduled task tomorrow\n\nSo they just want to confirm the setup is correct and wait for the automatic run tomorrow at 9am.\n\nI should confirm everything is set and ready for the scheduled task tomorrow.\n\nLet me just confirm and keep everything ready.\n","thinkingSignature":"c19610797fca5145dd573a31db8d186edac3ebdff95e95ee088d60a828c33f83"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，encode_params 用固定的，明天 9 点自动跑。\n\n配置确认完毕，等明天跑就行 ✅\n\n**明日 9:00 自动执行：**\n1. 跑 Sorftime VN Hair Clips 类目报告\n2. 筛选增长率 > 0 + 综合评分 ≥ 100 + 毛利率 ≥ 30%\n3. Top10 写入飞书表格\n4. 飞书通知你\n\n今晚准备好就行，明天看结果 👍"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1831,"output":169,"cacheRead":113728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115728,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779027562796,"responseId":"06590170d972474c449dca3dd6e29985"}}
