{"type":"message","id":"1fd79f62","parentId":"0163a51c","timestamp":"2026-05-17T14:23:45.567Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I'm a script or a cron job. They're questioning how the automated task would run. Let me think about this:\n\nIn the OpenClaw context, I am an AI agent (TTS agent). The \"scheduled task\" at 9am would be triggered by a cron job or heartbeat mechanism that wakes up this agent session.\n\nLooking at AGENTS.md and HEARTBEAT.md:\n- HEARTBEAT.md is empty (no checks)\n- There's a heartbeat system that periodically polls the agent\n\nBut there's no cron job configured yet. The user is right to question this - I said \"明天9点自动跑\"，but there's no actual cron mechanism set up yet.\n\nI should be honest - I'm an AI agent, not a cron job. The \"scheduled run\" would need to be set up as a cron job or heartbeat task that triggers the TTS agent to run the selection workflow. I don't have a built-in cron scheduler - I would need to set one up.\n\nLet me clarify with the user about how they want this to work. Should I set up a cron job? Should it be triggered by heartbeat? Or did they think this was already automated?\n\nI should be honest and say I need to set up the actual automation mechanism (cron or heartbeat), and ask how they want to proceed.\n","thinkingSignature":"bba8412eb1eb38700502e80916afa50c347a1c0c87266feb8bc71a50d369f212"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好问题。我是 AI Agent，不是 cron 脚本。\n\n\"明天 9 点自动跑\"这句话说得不严谨——实际上还没有设置定时触发器。\n\n需要确认：**你希望怎么触发明天的选品任务？**\n\n1. **Cron 定时任务** → 每天定时启动一个独立选品 session，跑完写入飞书后结束\n2. **心跳触发** → 利用 HEARTBEAT.md 机制，每天固定时间检查并跑选品\n3. **手动触发** → 你说\"跑\"的时候我再执行\n\n哪种方式你比较习惯？我可以帮你配。\n\n其实现在最现实的是**心跳触发**：在 HEARTBEAT.md 里写好选品流程，每天 8:30-9:00 之间触发一次就行。或者 cron 更精准。要哪个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":75,"output":435,"cacheRead":115776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116286,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779027793266,"responseId":"0659025196f342f8d3431d2ce29bf1c3"}}
